  "title": "🍓Part Time Snack Kiosk Assistants @ Central/Northeast | $12/hr | No experience needed!",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>🍓Part Time Snack Kiosk Assistants @ Central/Northeast | $12/hr | No experience needed!</strong></u></p><p>📍Location: Chinatown/Ang Mo Kio/Pasir Ris </p><p>💰Salary: $12/hr  </p><p>Public holidays double pay!  </p><p>🗓️Working days: 5 day work week (Between Mon-Sun) </p><p>🕑Shift hours: 9am-3pm / 11am-5pm / 4.30pm-10.30pm  </p><p>Job role: </p><ul><li><p>Assist with food and snack preparation, testing, and packing according to operational standards. </p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness of the work area while strictly following food safety and hygiene regulations. </p></li><li><p>Operate tea-making equipment efficiently and handled customer orders and cash transactions accurately and promptly. </p></li><li><p>Provide friendly and efficient customer service, ensuring a positive experience and professionally  addressing customer inquiries or concerns. </p></li></ul><p>Requirements: </p><ul><li><p>WSQ Food and Hygiene Certificate </p></li></ul><p>📥Interested? Send us your resume at 8032 2021 or email: admin@crew.sg </p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary. </p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified </p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet </p><p>EA 24C2435 </p>",
